Would you like a smoothie?

515
00:57:23,588 --> 00:57:24,953
Tea is fine.

516
00:57:29,761 --> 00:57:34,755
Okay. I look, I look. Stop. Look...

517
00:57:37,569 --> 00:57:39,298
And now I die.

518
00:57:44,876 --> 00:57:48,778
-You were really good.
-Do you know what a nightmare it is?

519
00:57:48,947 --> 00:57:53,384
I mean, you spend all this time
getting ready, ages getting ready...

520
00:57:53,552 --> 00:57:57,488
...drag yourself to this audition.
They look at you for two seconds...

521
00:57:57,689 --> 00:58:03,389
...and tell you that you're too ethnic,
or too classic, too something.

522
00:58:03,595 --> 00:58:05,495
Too ethnic?

523
00:58:06,131 --> 00:58:11,000
It means brunette.
And too classic means old.

524
00:58:11,169 --> 00:58:15,697
And too small, breasts.

525
00:58:17,342 --> 00:58:22,006
-Why do you do it, then?
-What? Give up show business?

526
00:58:38,730 --> 00:58:40,027
Come on!

527
00:58:50,675 --> 00:58:55,772
-Well, here. To your first run at the beach.
-Never again.

528
00:58:56,481 --> 00:59:00,212
-How's your shoulder? You okay?
-Yeah. Yeah, it's fine.

529
00:59:00,385 --> 00:59:04,321
No, you did really well.
You did really, really well.

530
00:59:18,637 --> 00:59:20,332
What was...

531
00:59:20,605 --> 00:59:24,302
...the best day of your life?

532
00:59:29,881 --> 00:59:31,473
Today.

533
00:59:34,052 --> 00:59:38,716
-What should we do later?
-I don't know. What do you want to do?

534
00:59:39,391 --> 00:59:40,824
Swim?

535
00:59:41,259 --> 00:59:42,817
Okay.

536
00:59:44,729 --> 00:59:46,560
Oh, my God!

537
00:59:47,198 --> 00:59:49,530
