01:09:01,986 --> 01:09:05,251
Yeah. Yeah. She is.

657
01:09:10,528 --> 01:09:15,556
Would you mind letting us
talk alone, sweetie?

658
01:09:16,000 --> 01:09:18,491
Grown-up things.

659
01:09:19,370 --> 01:09:23,568
-Don't we have to go?
-No, it's okay.

660
01:09:24,008 --> 01:09:25,475
We have time.

661
01:09:44,729 --> 01:09:47,163
Love humiliates you.

662
01:09:47,331 --> 01:09:49,697
Hatred cradles you.

663
01:09:50,501 --> 01:09:52,264
It's soothing.

664
01:09:54,372 --> 01:09:56,272
What did you say to her?

665
01:09:57,174 --> 01:10:00,439
