have an attraction for older men.

667
01:10:05,082 --> 01:10:07,676
No, it's not me.

668
01:10:07,852 --> 01:10:10,480
-You leave her alone.
-But it's such fun.

669
01:10:11,055 --> 01:10:12,784
Easy, but fun.

670
01:10:12,957 --> 01:10:16,393
In my present situation
I have to get fun where I can.

671
01:10:18,029 --> 01:10:21,123
God, how can you stand
to live with poor Claire?

672
01:10:21,299 --> 01:10:25,429
Did you know there's an entire order
