681
01:11:04,442 --> 01:11:07,411
...keep your bags packed.

682
01:11:08,980 --> 01:11:12,472
I don't feel like it.
I'm a stranger in my own house.

683
01:11:12,650 --> 01:11:15,676
You live here
and I stay here once in a while.

684
01:11:15,853 --> 01:11:18,583
-Maybe if you gave a little bit.
-I give.

685
01:11:18,756 --> 01:11:22,192
Why can't I give to her,
why can't I be here?

686
01:11:22,360 --> 01:11:26,592
-Because I work! Because I have a job.
-That's not fair.

687
01:11:26,831 --> 01:11:30,096
I give you everything you ask for
and it's not enough.

688
01:11:30,267 --> 01:11:33,759
No, not everything.
Not everything.

689
01:11:33,938 --> 01:11:36,600
You promised things would change.

690
01:11:36,774 --> 01:11:41,734
-Mark, I'm trying, you know I'm trying.
-Trying's not good enough.

691
01:11:41,912 --> 01:11:45,143
You're falling apart.
We are back to where we started.

692
01:11:45,316 --> 01:11:50,413
